e Empire!<br /><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/expanded-unuverse-pack\">Expanded UNUverse Pack</a> - More unique vehicles that flesh out the robust UNUverse!<br /><br />Try out these great UNU-Approved Content Packs!<br /><br /><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/dkz-automotive-industries\">DKZ Industries Automotive Branch</a> -&nbsp;A Great Assortment of Vintage and Classic Vehicles!</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/iv-mts-unu-bjorns-customs\">Bjorn's Customs</a> -&nbsp;Bjorn's customs is an addon to UNU Civil and UNU Parts. It includes aftermarket parts for the contractor and contractor xl.<br /><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/randall-agriculture-pack\">IV Farming</a> - A bunch of essential farming accesories!</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/syndicate-motor-foundry\">Syndicate Motor Foundry</a> -&nbsp;A content pack for Immersive Vehicles featuring a new brand of vehicles and parts!<br /><br /><a href=\"https://discord.gg/J9jY4Z6\">Join our Discord!<br /><br /></a><a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/Dr_prof_Luigi\">Support UNU on Patreon!<br /><br /></a><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/modpacks/fallout-mc\">Join the Official Server!</a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://bisecthosting.com/drprofluigi\"><img src=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/partners/custom-banners/f49d125b-80a8-4522-a819-1922543fb769.png\" alt=\"Shameless Bisecthosting Sponsorship\" width=\"900\" height=\"142\" /></a></p>",
